Package WATSSwingApp

Class WildAnimal

java.lang.Object
WATSSwingApp.WildAnimal
public class WildAnimal extends Object
Represents an individual wild animal in the tracking system.

This class stores attributes of a wild animal such as species, name, age, gender, weight, and health status. It provides accessor (getter) and mutator (setter) methods for each field. The WildAnimal class is primarily used by DatabaseManager to manage animal records.
